The paper proposes a new active learning approach using Generative Adversarial Networks (GAN), which are commonly used in machine learning for tasks such as image generation and classification. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also mentions numerical experiments, indicating a focus on empirical evaluation, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
